how to create an animation  ??
-----------------------------

@keyframes growProgressBar{ //define an animation with name grow...Bar and actions in percent
0% {
width: 0%;
background-color: red;
}
50% {
background-color: yellow;
}
100% {
width:88%;
background-color: green;
}
}


How do i use this???
-------------------------

.progressBar {
animation-name: growProgessBar;
animation-duration 10s;
animation-play-state: paused; // if no animation needed  -----u can start it by $('.progressBar').css('animation-play-state', 'running');
animation-fill-mode: forwards; //just makes sure that when the animation is finished, the element keeps the end keyframe properties
animation-delay:4s;  // starts after 4s onload
animation-iteration-count:3; //repeats 3times u can give infinite too
animation-direction:reverse; // reverse orderly execute the animation (from 100% to 0%)
                    alternate // order changes alternatively 0-100% then 100% to 0 and so on
animation-timing-function:ease-in // animation function it will control the speed based on fn

animation:growProgessBar 10s linear 2s 3 alternate; //short form
          animation-name-->duration--->timing function ---> delay ---> iter count ----> direction
}


using from to
--------------

@keyframes test{
from {   --------->0%
        width: 0%;
        background-color: red;
    }
to {------------> 100%
        width:88%;
        background-color: green;
    }
}
